snippet.title: Avadon 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Avadon 3: The Warborn, an indie fantasy adventure epic. Coming from Spiderweb Software for Windows, Mac, and iPad. Look for it in Fall, 2016!

Learn more at

http://www.spiderwebsoftware.com/avadon3/index.html
